{"thi-ap37:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap37:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap37:0.3":"7 Addhakasitheriapadana ","thi-ap37:1.1":"“Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap37:1.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap37:1.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap37:1.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap37:2.1":"Tadaham pabbajitvana, ","thi-ap37:2.2":"tassa buddhassa sasane; ","thi-ap37:2.3":"Samvuta patimokkhamhi, ","thi-ap37:2.4":"indriyesu ca pancasu. ","thi-ap37:3.1":"Mattannuni ca asane, ","thi-ap37:3.2":"yutta jagariyepi ca; ","thi-ap37:3.3":"Vasanti yuttayogaham, ","thi-ap37:3.4":"bhikkhunim vigatasavam. ","thi-ap37:4.1":"Akkosim dutthacittaham, ","thi-ap37:4.2":"ganiketi bhanim tada; ","thi-ap37:4.3":"Tena papena kammena, ","thi-ap37:4.4":"nirayamhi apaccisam. ","thi-ap37:5.1":"Tena kammavasesena, ","thi-ap37:5.2":"ajayim ganikakule; ","thi-ap37:5.3":"Bahusova paradhina, ","thi-ap37:5.4":"pacchimaya ca jatiyam. ","thi-ap37:6.1":"Kasisu setthikulaja, ","thi-ap37:6.2":"brahmacaribalenaham; ","thi-ap37:6.3":"Acchara viya devesu, ","thi-ap37:6.4":"ahosim rupasampada. ","thi-ap37:7.1":"Disvana dassaniyam mam, ","thi-ap37:7.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","thi-ap37:7.3":"Ganikatte nivesesum, ","thi-ap37:7.4":"akkosanabalena me. ","thi-ap37:8.1":"Saham sutvana saddhammam, ","thi-ap37:8.2":"buddhasetthena desitam; ","thi-ap37:8.3":"Pubbavasanasampanna, ","thi-ap37:8.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap37:9.1":"Tadupasampadatthaya, ","thi-ap37:9.2":"gacchanti jinasantikam; ","thi-ap37:9.3":"Magge dhutte thite sutva, ","thi-ap37:9.4":"labhim dutopasampadam. ","thi-ap37:10.1":"Sabbakammam parikkhinam, ","thi-ap37:10.2":"punnam papam tatheva ca; ","thi-ap37:10.3":"Sabbasamsaramuttinna, ","thi-ap37:10.4":"ganikattanca khepitam. ","thi-ap37:11.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap37:11.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap37:11.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap37:11.4":"vasi homi mahamune. ","thi-ap37:12.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap37:12.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap37:12.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap37:12.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap37:13.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap37:13.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap37:13.3":"Nanam mama mahavira, ","thi-ap37:13.4":"uppannam tava santike. ","thi-ap37:14.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap37:14.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap37:14.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap37:15.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap37:15.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap37:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap37:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap37:16.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap37:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap37:17.1":"Ittham sudam addhakasi bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap37:18.1":"Addhakasitheriyapadanam sattamam. "}